Package: gggradient
Title: Scales for Gradient Fills in 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Harry", "Thompson", , "harry@mayesfield.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Scales to map continuous x or y data values onto the fill
    aesthetic, producing a gradient fill along an axis in a 'ggplot2' plot.
    Set continuous or binned scales that vary fill across individual shapes.
